                  <property name="labelHtml" type="string">&lt;html&gt;After you click on Finish, the configuration properties are written to the file
&lt;p&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;config/application.yaml&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Changes only come into effect after you restart the jvmguard server.</property>
